Modifications in this fork (all under Apache 2.0):
  - awx/customvars/        New Django app: role variable/tag/handler
                           extraction, location & subnet management,
                           aggregated host variables, survey generation.
  - awx/api/urls/          Additional REST API routes for the above.
  - awx/main/tasks/jobs.py post_run_hook for automatic role scanning
                           after each project (git) sync.
  - awx/main/tasks/receptor.py
                           Container-isolation bypass for docker-compose
                           based deployments.
  - deploy/                docker-compose stack, Dockerfiles, configuration.

